</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB7368AD859FFD63CB4FA8330CAFE0A" blockId="12.[151,1058,1337,1388]" pageId="12" pageNumber="971">
E t y m o l o g y: Thetrivialname, 
<emphasis id="B97CEA98D859FFD63E01FA83305CFE28" box="[546,611,1337,1358]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="971">versus</emphasis>
, is a Latin noun with a meaning of &quot;line&quot;; with reference to the narrow black line on the pronotal disc.
</paragraph>
